      "message": "At a high level I think we need to update target-fail-monitoring.md out in the docs repo and I\u0027d like to see an example of the json file change. Also, I agree in some cases an immediate quiesce makes sense but with some services, we actually don\u0027t want that. i.e a lot of services are built to recover fine after a systemd service restart. A BMC quiesce is a big deal and should be avoided in these cases.",
